
  Greninja    Water Type Pokémon

  It creates throwing stars out 
  of compressed water.  When it 
  spins them and throws them at 
  high speed, these stars can split 
  metal in two. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Froakie ► Frogadier ► Greninja

